overview: The user wanted to elevate the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app. The assistant began by thoroughly analyzing the existing
  design, identifying areas like the generic color palette, basic form elements,
  and lack of visual interest. A new sleep-themed aesthetic was introduced,
  featuring a calming indigo/purple/teal color scheme, decorative background
  elements, and redesigned UI components such as checkboxes, radio buttons,
  sliders, and progress bars. All questionnaire sections and the final report
  section were updated for consistent, polished styling. During the review, a
  console error related to null values being passed to input fields was
  identified and fixed by modifying the Input component to safely handle such
  values. The overall outcome is a significantly more professional, cohesive,
  and visually appealing application that aligns with a sleep health theme.
